- Long-term maintenance therapy for patients with bilateral micro or macronodular adrenal hyperplasia (idiopathic hyperaldosteronism).[L44602]



As spironolactone has antiandrogenic activity, its off-label uses include the treatment of hirsutism, female pattern hair loss, and adult acne vulgaris.[A178135, A261025]', '6221068904848', NULL, 3490, '2022-12-01', 0, 0, 0);
